"
" A configuration file for https://github.com/JugglerShu/XVim
"
"

" Comments
map gcc :xccmd commentAndUncommentCurrentLines<cr>

" Emulate CTRL-P
map <C-p> :xccmd openQuickly<cr>

" Duplicate line with typical vim shortcut (hacky)
map :t.<cr> yyp

" Case-insensitive searching.
set ignorecase
" But case-sensitive if expression contains a capital letter.
set smartcase

" Use the system pasteboard
set pasteboard

" Map <space>b to toggle a breakpoint at the current line
nmap <space>b :xccmd toggleBreakpointAtCurrentLine<CR>

" Better navigation
nmap H ^
nmap L $

" Window navigation
nmap <C-j> <C-w>j
nmap <C-k> <C-w>k
nmap <C-h> <C-w>h
nmap <C-l> <C-w>l

" Tab mappings
nmap ,tt :xccmd newTab<CR>
nmap ,tc :tabclose<CR>
